The paper deals with the stability of an algorithm used in solving polynomial systems, which involves linear algebra computations. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of cs.SC (Symbolic Computation), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SY (Systems and Control), or cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). Among these, cs.SC and cs.NA seem to be the most likely categories, as the paper deals with computations involving polynomials and linear algebra. The other categories are less likely, but still possible, as the paper may have implications for control systems or logic in computer science.
